ice.  If so, he must have got on the wrong side of somebody, so the ponzi scheme was ended.   All for the greater good (or evil).<BR/><BR/>But Bernie might have a few millions (billions) socked away somewhere safe, and while he may do a bit of jail time, it might not be so hard as you think unless somebody really is pissed off, and life will be good for him again when he gets out. Maybe he even bought some property in Paraguay and will do some ranching with Bush.<BR/><BR/>Things are rarely as they seem.</p>
