ognize what it was about and supported it, or something like it, before the war, then I will agree, he was the Feds bitch and the greenbacks a ruse to make it look like he was not, or even to make the National Banking Act even more lucrative for the banksters. <BR/><BR/>Just like FDR pretending to be against fascism with that hoax that business tried to replace him using Butler to head an army and take over the White House to foist the fascist NRA and AAA on people.<BR/><BR/>Thanks for the links.</p>
